{"tid":869485,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳20男生染手足口病","createTime":"2018-10-20T11:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T00:01:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"930916acdafa438155e29db2165c5ec0f556be59","tid":869485,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:20:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181020/20526517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181020%2F20526517&d=%2FRxmjVM7Z6W960Lqc4hsBQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=4d45abfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181020%2F20526517&h=86064cf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181020/20526517</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月20日 <br />\n<br />\n將軍澳20男生染手足口病<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181020/large/plkhycc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181020%2Flarge%2Fplkhycc.jpg&h=754ecef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將軍澳保良局甲子何玉清中學20名男學生感染手足口病。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】將軍澳保良局甲子何玉清中學20名男學生感染手足口病，全部人已求醫但毋須入院，現時情況穩定；其中一人的糞便樣本驗出腸病毒。衞生防護中心指，手足口病會令口腔潰瘍及手腳出疹等，10月至12月可能出現較小型的感染高峯，提醒公眾注意衞生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一人糞便驗出腸病毒<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心昨日公佈，保良局甲子何玉清中學有20名12至14歲男學生，自上月25日起出現發燒、口腔潰瘍、手腳出疹及水疱等病徵，5人曾到將軍澳醫院急症室求醫，15人向私家醫生求醫；其中一名學生的糞便樣本經化驗後，證實對腸病毒呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n中心發言人指，手足口病是常見於兒童的疾病，通常由腸病毒引起，病徵包括手掌、腳掌，以至身體其他部份如臀部及大腿出現斑丘疹或水疱，口腔亦可能出現水疱及潰瘍；亦有病人主要在口腔後部出現疼痛潰瘍，而手腳沒有紅疹。手足口病一般在5月至7月較活躍，10月至12月亦可能出現較小型高峯。<br />\n<br />\n中心呼籲公眾注意衞生，包括保持空氣流通，雙手被沾污後應洗淨雙手。<br />\n<br />\n■記者袁樂婷  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n不滿資方刻薄　港龍空服員或罷工<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n囚犯控訴　當值四個月無假放　 指懲教拒調查　被警告勿搞事"},{"pid":"5a86995242de18a747b5ade0872df9e4f79c56f0","tid":869485,"uid":704,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:25:54.000Z","msg":"全部男生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc505507d037448f16ce67be7182ae3fb5f2980","tid":869485,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37d4885c7a6b56e5749f7587cf6102ece3c8e807","tid":869485,"uid":44725,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/20/GujbsQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F20%2FGujbsQ.jpg&h=c20567df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0da1185d96a0508c9f6026cea048761893c55d08","tid":869485,"uid":35946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:34:16.000Z","msg":"人型蜈蚣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6ccef0f7866c36b9d438fdf6688ae1b06b02ae","tid":869485,"uid":28624,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"GAY<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471b94eb8876fe966db357ba239aaebdea626ba4","tid":869485,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:40:21.000Z","msg":"手足口病主要透過接觸患者的鼻或喉嚨分泌物、唾液、穿破的水疱或糞便，或觸摸受污染的物件而傳播。患者在病發首星期最具傳染性，而病毒可在其糞便中存活數星期。"},{"pid":"c009e982f5e89b637bbfe45ea50501b65f75522e","tid":869485,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"以為幼稚園先會大規模爆發"},{"pid":"0da04d5492229a8fdec6f07480f4df9b43fdc996","tid":869485,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"個標題好gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5fdf39e2980276f2ed9a03c50e948ee6c6a13e","tid":86